### `Data`

```typescript
interface Data {
  voucher: Voucher;
  owner_profile: Profile;
  redeemer_profile: RedeemerProfile;
  my_ticket: MyTicket;
  tickets: MyTicket[];
}

interface Voucher {
  voucher_id: string;
  amount_baht: string;
  redeemed_amount_baht: string;
  member: number;
  status: "active" | "redeemed" | "expired";
  link: string;
  detail: string;
  expire_date: number;
  type: "R" | "F";
  redeemed: number;
  available: number;
}

interface Profile {
  full_name: string;
}

interface RedeemerProfile {
  mobile_number: string;
}

interface MyTicket {
  mobile: string;
  update_date: number;
  amount_baht: string;
  full_name: string;
  profile_pic: string | null;
}
```
